Invocation Name: fact genei
des:
Ask for Fact genei, and learn about what really matters, like dark matter.

Fact genei provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you smarter.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Fact genei" or "Alexa, open Fact genei to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
